advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
description:
P.F. Chang’s puts the entire restaurant experience into one delicious iPhone app. Place an order, make a reservation, find a location – it’s all inside. 

There are also a few things inside you may not expect. Wondering what dish goes best with your Chinese Zodiac? Discover your ideal meal with the Dish of Destiny feature. Needing some direction from Confucius? You can crack open a fortune cookie or create your own fortunes and share them with someone special.

So whether you want to make a reservation or are craving P.F. Chang’s to go, you’ll have everything you need right at your fingertips in one delicious app.

• Find your nearest P.F. Chang’s
• View the full P.F. Chang’s menu (including Lunch and Dinner)
• Place a takeout order – create a new order or select a previous order to enjoy again
• Make a reservation
• Sign-in to an existing account or create a new P.F. Chang’s account for ordering
• Discover your Dish of Destiny based on your Chinese Zodiac
• Get Words of Wisdom from the fortune cookie builder
• Learn about new events and promotions
• Share all of your favorites to Facebook and Twitter
